data.chText: （尤指新的或艰苦的）努力，尝试
data.enText: an attempt to do sth, especially sth new or difficult
Please make every endeavour to arrive on time.

data.chText: 在科学探索领域的进步
data.enText: advances in the field of scientific endeavour

data.chText: 经纪人应以最大的努力来推动其演艺人的事业发展。
data.enText: The manager is expected to use his or her best endeavours to promote the artist's career.
to try very hard to do sth

data.chText: 我将竭尽全力报效祖国。
data.enText: I will endeavour to do my best for my country.

means: (尤指新的或艰苦的)努力，尝试

ex.chText: 抬起这只沉重的箱子很费力。
ex.enText: It takes quite an effort to lift this heavy box.

ex.chText: 你的付出一定会有所收获。
ex.enText: Your effort is bound to be rewarded.

ex.chText: 每个人都应为减少污染尽一份力。
ex.enText: Everybody should make an effort to reduce pollution.

synonyms.bx: 指做某事的尝试，尤含大量辛苦劳作或毅力。

ex.enText: He has been working with diligence.

ex.chText: 她的勤奋为我们所有人树立了榜样。
ex.enText: Her diligence has set an example to us all.

ex.chText: 他尽一切努力还清债务。
ex.enText: He made every endeavour to pay off the debt.

ex.chText: 我试图达成和解的努力全部落空了。
ex.enText: My endeavours to bring about a settlement ended in vain .

synonyms.bx: 指对困难或新鲜事物的尝试。

tr: earnest and conscientious activity intended to do or accomplish something
example: made an effort to cover all the reading material
wished him luck in his endeavor
she gave it a good try

tr: a purposeful or industrious undertaking (especially one that requires effort or boldness)
example: he had doubts about the whole enterprise
we endeavor to make our customers happy

value.boxr_value: in AM, use 美国英语用 endeavor

value.def: If you endeavour to do something, you try very hard to do it.

example.ex: I will endeavour to arrange it...
They are endeavouring to protect trade union rights.
example.tran: 他们在竭力捍卫工会的权利。

value.def: An endeavour is an attempt to do something, especially something new or original.

example.ex: His first endeavours in the field were wedding films.
example.tran: 他初涉这个领域时做的是婚礼摄影。

example.ex: ...the benefits of investment in scientific endeavour.
example.tran: 在科学领域投资的收益

gramarinfo.label: usu with supp, oft N to-inf

value.tran: (尤指新的或创造性事物的)努力，尝试
